{"tid":464146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日9屍命案身分全確認　大多是「邊緣女」","createTime":"2017-11-10T08:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T11:15:25.000Z","uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"236dd9bc80ca7847e4b797ff3a6f57b92b03408f","tid":464146,"uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"震驚日本全社會的神奈川座間市9屍命案，警視廳在今日凌晨發布9名死者的身分已經確認完畢，9名死者來自東京、埼玉、福島等地區，年齡為15~26歲，而當中大多數都是「邊緣女」。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《朝日新聞》報導，9名死者當中除了一名是男性，其他8名全是女性。27歲主嫌白石隆浩供稱，他透過推特與這些受害女子接觸，而這些女性多在推特上透露悲觀、遭霸凌、對人生無望等訊息，自認是社會邊緣人，而白石向她們傳遞訊息回應「一起死吧」，來引誘進到白石的屋內，最後白石行兇殺人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171110/640_b638484e1fa7461933dfe7afe276471a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171110%2F640_b638484e1fa7461933dfe7afe276471a.jpg&h=e23f4c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171110/1238443/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171110%2F1238443%2F&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7E4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=87177fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171110%2F1238443%2F&h=0e64d0bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171110/1238443/</a>"},{"pid":"126594cb8429bfe47c63381bb93d6434d59a1a88","tid":464146,"uid":32818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"下 唔係姦殺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e5d9e97976ed597fd98f598672cc1cc9d08b5e","tid":464146,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"哇屌，全部開名開樣"},{"pid":"e8454f2be78f599fe6cd0f2b26ff12b962147e90","tid":464146,"uid":29898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11: